<h1>Policy + Prompt Pack (Starter)</h1>
<div class="card"><pre><code>- Human-in-the-loop for anything external
- Red/Amber/Green data classification; only Green in consumer models
- Prefer client enterprise tenancy; otherwise use local/offline tools
- Cite sources; run chain-of-verification for facts
- Keep audit trail (prompt, output, reviewer, decision)</code></pre></div>

<h2>Prompt Patterns (copy & adapt)</h2>
<div class="grid two">
  <div class="card"><b>Role-Task-Context-Constraints-Format</b><pre><code>You are a [role].
Task: [what to do].
Context: [facts, source].
Constraints: [brand, policy].
Output format: [bullet spec].</code></pre></div>
  <div class="card"><b>Summarize-Then-Decide</b><pre><code>1) Summarize the input faithfully (no advice).
2) Given the summary, decide [X] and justify with quotes.</code></pre></div>
  <div class="card"><b>Extract-Structure</b><pre><code>Extract fields into valid JSON: { "field": "type", ... }.
If missing, use null. Return ONLY JSON.</code></pre></div>
  <div class="card"><b>Compare-Against-Rubric</b><pre><code>First critique draft vs rubric. Then rewrite to meet rubric.</code></pre></div>
</div>
</div></body></html>
